{"type": "article", "id": 13385, "title": "麦当劳新型设计", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-12T07:14:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001737xpuwZoDtCa1fWjHP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t麦当劳乱七八糟的外带包装让设计师为他们操碎了心，最近，Jessica Stoll 设计了一款新的包装袋，新包装袋和现在的包装袋外观上差别不大，但它可以变身“立在桌上”，“拎在手里”，“坐在腿上”三种“姿势”，分别方便不同情形下用户的使用习惯，比如，当对折方形包装袋的边角，可以把下部变成尖尖的样子，插在缝隙里面，不容易倾倒。这是<a href=\"http://www.jessicastoll.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141206aHb7Wm32cnNle0Vt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141206Kp4h7uHCsA9XoGt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141207e4J62fXujNcOEiRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141207Gci5wbgN4ZU0aedR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61369193\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141208CVgA0QvOufFpo8L2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141209tlAgK645MyBszawn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141209rOW7Bn4Y6evEupNR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141210I3uQLxbKh01vZroP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53300733\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}